<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF946A2BF82290F9175FBC0A" pageId="111" pageNumber="869" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF946A2BF82290F9175FBC0A" blockId="111.[2012,2609,1499,1927]" pageId="111" pageNumber="869">
Previously treated within either 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF946A2BF65690F91608BDDB" baseAuthorityName="J. Fischer" baseAuthorityYear="1829" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Plecotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="111" pageNumber="869" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="austriacus">P. austriacus</taxonomicName>
or 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF946A2BF7BC909116C2BDDB" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1758" box="[2112,2242,1736,1769]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Plecotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="111" pageNumber="869" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="auritus">P. auritus</taxonomicName>
, but recently elevated to species level based on morphological and molecular data. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
